commits.commitMessage:
Use usbpath fwdld option instead of the serial number

Determining the serial number and passing that to fwdld
is quite inefficiant since:
- on some devices (early dev stages) the serial number might
  not be available from USB
- if it is available, some devices such as the WP85 shows that
  the number is not necessarily the same between normal mode
  and boot&hold mode

Resolves: LETOOLS-940 LETOOLS-1044
Change-Id: Id25057dd012649e4f13dc675c075d7f8b461f7c8
commits.subject: Use usbpath fwdld option instead of the serial number
